    {
        "content": "<p>alexcrichton created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13017#discussion_r3060449550\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Given how subtle this is I'd prefer to not duplicate the <code>get</code> method above. Would it be possible to refactor the trait methods or un-generalize the <code>NameMap</code> in general if the full generic <code>K</code> type parameter isn't needed?</p>\n</blockquote>",
